org.walkingarchive.backend.model.card
Class Deck

java.lang.Object
  org.walkingarchive.backend.model.card.Deck

public class Deck
extends java.lang.Object

A Deck object represents a Magic: The Gathering trading card deck A Deck is made up of a collection of Cards, with a User as its owner, and a name given by the user.
